title: south indian style
review: dedicated to lord venkateshwar, this is built in a typical south indian style of architecture with white exteriors.

title: Tirupati in Rishikesh!
review: Properly built in the south Indian style and a change for me in Rishikesh. Venkateswara Swamy temple was a short visit and it was on the way from Rishikesh bus stop to Laxman jhula. I still remember a man was playing Nagaswaram when I visited the temple. Mindblowing!
